{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Create yOur HerO's jOurney</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you won\u2019t just play\u2014you\u2019ll create. The world of Obu becomes a sandbox for your imagination as you design and customize your own character. Shape every aspect of their appearance, abilities, and playstyle. Want to be a high-tech warrior wielding futuristic weapons or a sorceress mastering elemental magic? The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with different powers, mix and match abilities, and fine-tune your character\u2019s skills to suit your unique approach. The demo highlights the flexibility and creativity central to the full game, letting you discover how your character\u2019s strengths evolve as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/gif004.gif?t=1737631900\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DiscOver yOur HerO's pOtential</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Obu</i> combines fast-paced combat, exploration, and a rich crafting system. In addition to customizing your character, you'll dive into action-packed battles, harness magic, and build everything from weapons to vehicles. The demo introduces you to the core mechanics\u2014combat, exploration, and, most importantly, crafting and character creation. Explore the endless world and uncover hidden mysteries as you mold your own path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/extras/gif002.gif?t=1737631900\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737631900","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737631900","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/